"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話PS4個龜速HDD要stream未來30秒嘅資源<br />\nPS5個高速SSD只需要stream定1秒嘅資源<br />\n<br />\n跟住吹到連遮擋剔除嘅快取都可以唔使放入RAM<br />\n轉個視角等1秒由SSD過返入返RAM然後再render<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我玩開60FPS嘅講緊16ms要render好1個frame<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd1e2234ee4c9be41146b2db42f97be3936c7141","tid":2021180,"uid":109923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fe7a84429699ba1ef55ae93312a68599f4a5e834","tid":2021180,"uid":130568,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"22174269efdcf00357f34a556dfb7fd3d27a4168","tid":2021180,"uid":109923,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T14:47:02.000Z","msg":"正常發揮，PS4年代都係咁嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nequivalent效能行equivalent畫質都係PC贏<br />\n低畫質、低FPS玩隻GAME，跟住打飛機話console最佳化做得好好<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9OE2iI7OLh8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9OE2iI7OLh8&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=a053d22f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9OE2iI7OLh8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gGf4SVWEw2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgGf4SVWEw2g&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=beebe637\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gGf4SVWEw2g</a><br />\n<br />\n明明console可以吹奏嘅優勢就係「價錢平」同「冇外掛」<br />\n死都要同PC鬥效能唔知做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T14:54:06.000Z","msg":"尷尬啲乜? 點解會變咗PS5勁過PC?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:04:23.000Z","msg":"講緊console嘅PC equivalent<br />\n所以條片用緊750ti嚟比PS4"},{"pid":"81e924bc92d4fa932e269f8572ebb4ec728e5bf4","tid":2021180,"uid":94835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:09:35.000Z","msg":"尷尬"},{"pid":"540bc7a0a07ebef406ae6961ffea1f5f25de3c8a","tid":2021180,"uid":57,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"quote":{"pid":"fe7a84429699ba