56dfb7fd3d27a4168","tid":2021180,"uid":109923,"like":51,"dislike":0,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T14:47:02.000Z","msg":"正常發揮，PS4年代都係咁嫁啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nequivalent效能行equivalent畫質都係PC贏<br />\n低畫質、低FPS玩隻GAME，跟住打飛機話console最佳化做得好好<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9OE2iI7OLh8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9OE2iI7OLh8&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=a053d22f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9OE2iI7OLh8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gGf4SVWEw2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgGf4SVWEw2g&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=beebe637\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gGf4SVWEw2g</a><br />\n<br />\n明明console可以吹奏嘅優勢就係「價錢平」同「冇外掛」<br />\n死都要同PC鬥效能唔知做乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T14:54:06.000Z","msg":"尷尬啲乜? 點解會變咗PS5勁過PC?"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:11:34.000Z","msg":"之前有個post有幾個人講到PS5靠SSD就可以勁過PC<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pjFhomV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpjFhomV.png&h=dd2015d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n視野剔除呢種最基本嘅嘅optimization方法變咗要靠高速ssd先做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n連十年前嘅online game都用緊更進階嘅遮擋剔除，連前方視野被遮擋嘅物件都剔除埋<br />\n啲人喺2020年仲吹緊視野剔除<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5h4QgDBwQhc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5h4QgDBwQhc&d=bavYdQ8E6vkyiKAGb1dQCQZxBlA1GgcQN30t83kccHY%3D&h=87205712\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5h4QgDBwQhc</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過執口水尾，唔識扮識都唔係第一次<br />\n不論pc定ps4遊戲都係high poly 做完detail，再pre bake 成low poly上各種normal mapping <br />\n唔講以為pc直接塞high poly入game<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />得ps4先用low poly上各類法線貼圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nLOD 調校到pc版嘅low，狂pop in=做得好，我心諗你玩pc版將LOD set做low咪一撚樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GKybsQA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGKybsQA.png&h=7a28f2be&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bbf39eff2600ee3b928ff1268ed7c347e251e67a","tid":2021180,"uid":94828,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:44:46.000Z","msg":"打臉打到啪啪聲<br />\n又話ssd好勁 pc追唔上？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11f788a5261ee8dd343a4d6a720b93d725edb37","tid":2021180,"uid":13100,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"bbf39eff2600ee3b928ff1268ed7c347e251e67a","tid":2021180,"uid":94828,"like":6,"dislike":5,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-17T15:44:46.000Z","msg":"打臉打到啪啪聲<br />\n又話ssd好勁 pc追唔上？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T14:45:01.000Z","msg":"隻SONY SSD會唔會賣出街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果PC最頂級GPU + 最頂級SSD,咁當然勁過PS5啦<br />\n問題係幾多錢唧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b5a63ea812c475bd063ba688edb1e65d31c2e0","tid":2021180,"uid":198929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-20T15:31:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/smn4srR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https